original_title: Scalps II: The Return of DJ
overview: 4 friends head off to do some partying near the old Indian Caves. An innocent weekend of fun turns in to an utter nightmare when they accidentally stumble upon the old Black Trees and dig up an arrow head on the land. D.J., the final victim of “Black Claw” awakens and continues the legacy of Black Claw’s revenge. Will anyone survive this night from hell?
title: Scalps II: The Return of DJ
